<HR><H2>Back up problem solved</H2>
<H3>daemon@ATHENA.MIT.EDU (Sun Jul  2 19:39:45 2000
)</H3>
<PRE>
From: "Peter Bombard" &lt;pbombard@altavista.net&gt;
